{"tid":1266073,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 粉嶺撚請入！阻止嘉福工聯會自動當選","createTime":"2019-06-29T12:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T16:20:41.000Z","uid":158504,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"20ec3015336e67fb9d08b158ddf55dc962ba1061","tid":1266073,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1265840/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1265840/page/1</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盛福 工聯會已經做左10年<br />\n上届更加係自動當選<br />\n呢度冇嘢多，廢老多（日日喺下面露天劇場 妹下妹下賭錢）<br />\n真係唔想溫和達條撚樣今年又自動當選<br />\n<br />\n上屆立法會 呢度民主派票佔57% 當中最多嗰個仲要係梁頌恆<br />\n絕對係可以打得贏<br />\n票數 名單<br />\n807 鄧家彪<br />\n693 陳克勤<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">620 梁頌恆<br />\n531 張超雄<br />\n441 楊岳橋<br />\n424 陳志全<br />\n371 梁國雄<br />\n363 林卓廷</span></strong><br />\n248 方國珊<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">230 陳云根</span></strong><br />\n225 葛珮帆<br />\n212 容海恩<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">194 范國威</span></strong><br />\n147 李梓敬<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">145 鄭家富</span></strong><br />\n43 麥嘉晉<br />\n43 李偲嫣<br />\n37 侯志強<br />\n23 黃琛喻<br />\n9 廖添誠<br />\n5 梁金成<br />\n2 陳玉娥<br />\n<br />\n悲傷還悲傷<br />\n希望大家通傳 叫民主派派多個人落嚟<br />\n光復多個地方<br />\n<br />\n利申：嘉盛撚 一陣落去默哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad6580d16f71307ae19e040ab25c60727405b85","tid":1266073,"uid":149137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20ec3015336e67fb9d08b158ddf55dc962ba1061","tid":1266073,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1265840/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1265840/page